@server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5037

### Users - Get All
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/user
Accept: application/json

### Users - Register/Create User
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "waiter1",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": 2
}

### Auth - Login (JWT)
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "waiter1",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Categories - Get All
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/category
Accept: application/json

### Categories - Create Category
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryName": "Tatlılar",
  "description": "Nefis Restoran Tatlıları"
}

### Products - Get All (with Category Filter)
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/product?categoryId=1
Accept: application/json

### Products - Create Product
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Fırın Sütlaç",
  "description": "Karadeniz usulü fırın sütlaç",
  "price": 85.00,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/sutlac.jpg",
  "categoryId": 1
}

### Orders - Get Active Orders
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/order/active
Accept: application/json

### Orders - Create Order
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableNumber": 3,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "note": "Bol fındıklı olsun"
    }
  ]
}

### Orders - Update Status
PATCH {{server_HostAddress}}/api/order/UpdateStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "newStatus": 1
}

### Tables - Get All Tables
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/table
Accept: application/json

### Tables - Update Table Occupied Status
PATCH {{server_HostAddress}}/api/table/3/status
Content-Type: application/json

true

### Tables - Send Service Request (Garson Çağır)
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/table/3/service-request
Content-Type: application/json

"CallWaiter"
